Installing the SQL formatter in your vim install.

Edit your .vimrc

set nocp
filetype plugin on

Install the Align.vba

vim Align.vba
:so %
:q

Install the SQL stuff

cp sqlutil_400/autoload/SQLUtilities.vim ~/.vim/autoload
cp sqlutil_400/plugin/SQLUtilities.vim ~/.vim/plugin

We use a small modification to the original 4.00 versions
of the sql scripts which sets the text width to 132 instead
of using the terminal width for splitting the queries in a
known way and not in a terminal dependend way.
